---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import PageHero from '../components/PageHero.astro';
import Breadcrumb from '../components/Breadcrumb.astro';
import SectionHeading from '../components/SectionHeading.astro';

const schema = {
  '@context': 'https://schema.org',
  '@type': 'Service',
  name: 'Exterior Painting',
  provider: { '@type': 'GeneralContractor', name: 'Purpose Construction', url: 'https://purposeconstructionco.com' },
  areaServed: { '@type': 'State', name: 'Texas', containedIn: { '@type': 'Country', name: 'United States' } },
  description: 'Exterior painting across East Texas — power washing, surface prep, primer, and premium exterior paint for house exteriors, trim, siding, and porches across East Texas.',
};
---
<BaseLayout
  title="Exterior Painting East Texas | Purpose Construction"
  description="Exterior painting across East Texas — power washing, proper prep, primer, and premium paint for house exteriors, trim, and porches. Purpose Construction serves East Texas. Call (936) 555-5555."
  schema={schema}
>
  <Breadcrumb items={[{ label: 'Services', href: '/services' }, { label: 'Exterior Services', href: '/exterior-services' }, { label: 'Exterior Painting', href: '/exterior-painting' }]} />
  <PageHero title="Exterior Painting in East Texas" subtitle="Power washing, proper prep, primer, and premium exterior paints that hold up to East Texas sun, rain, and humidity — fresh color that lasts for years." tag="Exterior Service" />

  <section class="section-padding bg-warm-50">
    <div class="container-wide px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-12 lg:grid-cols-2 lg:items-center">
        <div>
          <SectionHeading tag="Exterior Painting" title="Prep Work That Makes the Paint Last" />
          <div class="space-y-4 text-base leading-relaxed text-charcoal-600">
            <p>Exterior paint in East Texas faces conditions that accelerate failure — intense UV exposure, high humidity that drives moisture behind paint film, mildew growth from the warm wet climate, and frequent heavy rainfall that pounds surfaces. Purpose Construction's exterior painting process starts with thorough power washing to remove mildew, chalk, and dirt, followed by proper scraping, sanding, caulking, and priming before any finish coat is applied. Skipping these steps is why exterior paint jobs fail in two years instead of lasting ten.</p>
            <p>We use premium exterior paints and primers rated for humid Southern climates — products with mildewcide additives and flexible formulations that expand and contract with the substrate through East Texas temperature swings without cracking or peeling. The right product on a properly prepped surface will protect your home and hold color significantly longer than a rushed, low-bid paint job.</p>
            <p>We paint full home exteriors, trim and fascia, wood siding, brick accents, and porch decking across East Texas and Angelina County. Color consultation is included — we help you choose a color combination that works with your home's architecture and your neighborhood.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="mt-6 flex gap-4">
            <a href="/contact" class="btn-primary">Get a Free Estimate</a>
            <a href="/exterior-services" class="btn-outline">All Exterior Services</a>
          </div>
        </div>
        <img src="https://placehold.co/640x480/2a2520/555?text=Exterior+Painting" alt="Exterior painting across East Texas by Purpose Construction" class="rounded-xl shadow-hero" width="640" height="480" loading="lazy" decoding="async" />
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section-padding bg-white border-t border-warm-200">
    <div class="container-wide px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <SectionHeading tag="What's Included" title="Exterior Painting Services" align="center" />
      <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-4 sm:grid-cols-3 lg:grid-cols-4">
        {['House Exterior', 'Trim & Fascia', 'Siding Painting', 'Porches & Decks', 'Power Washing', 'Surface Prep', 'Primer', 'Premium Exterior Paint'].map(item => (
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2 rounded-lg border border-warm-200 bg-warm-50 px-4 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-charcoal-700">
            <span class="h-1.5 w-1.5 flex-shrink-0 rounded-full bg-brand-red" aria-hidden="true"></span>{item}
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section-padding-sm bg-warm-50 border-t border-warm-200">
    <div class="container-wide px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <SectionHeading tag="Related Services" title="Related Exterior Services" />
      <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3">
        {[{ label: 'Siding Installation', href: '/siding-installation' }, { label: 'Interior Painting', href: '/interior-painting' }, { label: 'Exterior Services', href: '/exterior-services' }].map(link => (
          <a href={link.href} class="rounded-lg border border-warm-200 bg-white px-5 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-charcoal-700 shadow-card hover:border-brand-red-mid hover:text-charcoal-900 transition-all duration-200">{link.label} →</a>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section-padding bg-gradient-red">
    <div class="container-mid px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <h2 class="display-md text-white mb-4">Ready to Repaint Your Home's Exterior?</h2>
      <p class="mx-auto mb-8 max-w-xl text-base text-white/80">Contact Purpose Construction for a free exterior painting estimate. We serve Lufkin and all of East Texas.</p>
      <div class="flex flex-col items-center gap-4 sm:flex-row sm:justify-center">
        <a href="/contact" class="btn-ghost px-8 py-4">Get a Free Quote</a>
        <a href="tel:9365555555" class="text-sm font-semibold text-white/70 hover:text-white transition-colors duration-150">(936) 555-5555</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
